data.description: Check out this NEARLY NEW AMAZING duplex in a highly desired neighborhood with no HOA fees!   Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, and a nice sized pantry combined with dining room that leads out to the brand NEW Trex Deck built 2023!   The upper level has 3 spacious bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms.  Enjoy vaulted ceilings in the primary bedroom with extra windows for great lighting, a walk-in closet as well as an attached full bathroom.   Make your appointment to see this beautiful home today! ALL OFFERS DUE BY 12/1/23 BY 2PM!
